import React from 'react'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import VideoContainer from './VideoContainer'

const Main = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{height:'1000px'}}>
      <VideoContainer/>
      <section>SectionBanner1</section>
      <section>Section Category</section>
      <section>SectionBanner2</section>
      <section>Newsletter Wrapper</section>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Main
